# Avatar Images Directory

Place avatar images in this directory. Supported formats: JPG, PNG, WebP

Example structure:
- avatar-default.jpg (default avatar image)
- user1.jpg
- user2.jpg
- team-member.png

Reference images in code using:
```typescript
import { getAvatarImage } from "@/utils/imagePaths";
const imageUrl = getAvatarImage("default");
```

Or add new images to `src/utils/imagePaths.ts`:
```typescript
export const IMAGE_PATHS = {
  avatars: {
    default: "/images/avatars/avatar-default.jpg",
    user1: "/images/avatars/user1.jpg", // Add new entries here
  },
};
```

